"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Register For Slashing Insurance\\n\\nEach validator can register for slashing insurance at their discretion. The steps for the validator to register for slashing insurance are here:\\n\\n\\nhttps://github.com/interstate-labs/proposer-commitment-network-dev/blob/main/scripts/urc/README.md\\n\\n\\nRegistering for slashing insurance allows users to slash if their preconfirmation is missed and increases the chances of a user signing up for preconfirmations. Certain users may only send preconfirmations if the slash insurance for a certain slot exceeds a certain amount. Interstate can provide slashing collateral on your behalf, please reach out to inquire!\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/validator/slashing_insurance_registration#register-for-slashing-insurance\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n<p>Each validator can register for slashing insurance at their discretion. The steps for the validator to register for slashing insurance are here:</p>\\n<p><a href=\\\"https://github.com/interstate-labs/proposer-commitment-network-dev/blob/main/scripts/urc/README.md\\\">https://github.com/interstate-labs/proposer-commitment-network-dev/blob/main/scripts/urc/README.md</a></p>\\n<p>Registering for slashing insurance allows users to slash if their preconfirmation is missed and increases the chances of a user signing up for preconfirmations. Certain users may only send preconfirmations if the slash insurance for a certain slot exceeds a certain amount. Interstate can provide slashing collateral on your behalf, please reach out to inquire!</p>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/validator/slashing_insurance_registration.mdx#register-for-slashing-insurance\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nEach validator can register for slashing insurance at their discretion. The steps for the validator to register for slashing insurance are here:\\nhttps://github.com/interstate-labs/proposer-commitment-network-dev/blob/main/scripts/urc/README.md\\nRegistering for slashing insurance allows users to slash if their preconfirmation is missed and increases the chances of a user signing up for preconfirmations. Certain users may only send preconfirmations if the slash insurance for a certain slot exceeds a certain amount. Interstate can provide slashing collateral on your behalf, please reach out to inquire!\",\"title\":\"Register For Slashing Insurance\",\"titles\":[]}]}}"
